{"word":"G4960 - συστοιχέω - systoichéō - soos-toy-kheh'-o - Answer to","sections":[{"paragraph":"<strong>மூல வார்த்தை / Original: </strong><span class=\"hebrewOrGreek\">συστοιχέω</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>எழுத்துமாற்றம் / Transliteration: </strong><span class=\"transliteration\">systoichéō</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>ஒலிபெயர்ப்பு / Phonetic: </strong><span class=\"phonetic\">soos-toy-kheh'-o</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>சுருக்க விளக்கம் / Short Definition: </strong><span class=\"short-definition\">Answer to</span>"},{"paragraph":"<span class=\"parts-of-speech\"><strong>இலக்கண சொல்வகை / Part(s) of speech: </strong>Verb / வினைச்சொல்</span>"},{"paragraph":"வினைச்சொல் - சரி"},{"paragraph":"to stand or march in the same row (file) with"},{"paragraph":"<span class=\"original-in-english\"><strong>ஆங்கில மூலம் / Original in English: </strong>From <a href=\"#/G4862 - σύν - sýn - soon/4862\">G4862</a> and <a href=\"#/G4748 - στοιχέω - stoichéō - stoy-kheh'-o/4748\">G4748</a>; to <i>file together</i> (as soldiers in ranks), that is, (figuratively) to <i>correspond</i> to: - answer to.</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>தொடர்புடைய எண்கள் / Cognate: </strong><a href=\"#/G4747/4747\">G4747</a>, <a href=\"#/G4748/4748\">G4748</a>, <a href=\"#/G4960/4960\">G4960</a>"}]}